## Match predictions
- Exact score: 5 pts
- Result + goal difference (non-draws only): 3 pts
- Non-exact draw (both predicted draw): 2 pts
- Correct result only: 1 pt

## Scorer bonus
- Correct: +2 pts
- Wrong: -1 pt

## Knockout multiplier
- Stages: round_of_32, round_of_16, quarter_final, semi_final, third_place, final
- Multiplier: 1.5× (CEIL)

## Season predictions
- Champion: 30 pts
- Best player: 25 pts
- Top scorer: 20 pts
- Locked after first match
